{"tid":1631571,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"見到有巴打話我地誤認咗啲唔係我地做嘅嘢（辱宗教之類），有冇方法破解？","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T00:03:17.000Z","uid":33769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"866e5865445d57b70277e6d0a57d27f0c5c3b537","tid":1631571,"uid":33769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"燒書局，毀文物，毀市民車，辱宗教，擺明黑警做！你哋點解自己認哂佢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631273\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631273</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n人地都做埋啲嘢幾明顯下，一字排開叫我地割席<br />\n連登又咁多分化po，係想我哋割席<br />\n突然間呢幾日無乜狗出嚟搞我地？咁筍？<br />\n講到明和平遊行，都突然間出現咁多對我地不利嘅利為？<br />\n有鬼係入面搞嘢係咪一個合理懷疑呀<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要諗個破解方法。<br />\n例如整翻個聲明，好似之前個不自殺聲明咁<br />\n講明大家絕對唔會做啲咩得唔得？（搶掠等等）<br />\n或者有冇其他好啲嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等高手出招"},{"pid":"7f14b4a288de0126b0b58fea6a400f34e4216e30","tid":1631571,"uid":33769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:54.000Z","msg":"無idea?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742e6c8dba7e8e19f141c5090a76fe345de9af91","tid":1631571,"uid":33769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"腦閉塞，乜都諗唔到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5361673885c4b8e15d66cabe09763c9bd575b457","tid":1631571,"uid":33769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:03:17.000Z","msg":"無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}